      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Hey Arnie!


    If you could spare a moment of your time, we''d be delighted
    if you responded to our 5-minute survey about your time dining at Chick-Fill-Et.


    Upon
    completion, you''ll recieve a digital coupon for 20% off your next Chick-Fill-Et.
    meal (valid for two weeks)!


    Our pleasure,

    Chick-Fill-Et.'
