  m_text: "Fresh Bait, \n\nCongratulations, you got the job!\n\nMy name's Bea Cutler,
    the new hire coordinator at Cut-Bait Inc. It's my job to train new employees
    like you to succeed during their first week on the job; you'll be hearing from
    me first thing every morning.\n\nScroll down for your personalized training below."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
