  m_text: "aelloway@bmail.com, \n\nDue to policy changes we've made in response to
    new laws, you're required to provide more information to validate your Bazin
    account.\n\nUntil this is done, any orders you make will be discarded. If you'd
    like to complete this step while we're still updating our website, please call:
    (833) 415-9007.\n\nThank you."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
