  m_text: "Guess what, Arnie?\n\nIn preparation of our recent appliance sale, \nStallmart
    locations near you overstocked on\nkitchen appliances.\n\nIn order to move these
    unsold products, Stallmart is shipping excess appliances to Stallmart Sales members,
    absolutely free! Scan the QR code below to apply while supplies last!\n\nOnce
    you finish, send to your Stallmart Sales friends!"
