  m_text: '


    Once you''re confident in whether the email is a scam, CLICK AND
    HOLD one of the buttons right of the email''s title to make a final decision:


    To
    send a legitimate email, use the GREEN ENVELOPE.


    To discard a scam, use
    the RED TRASH CAN.


    You''ll recieve a $20 dollar reward per correct decision,
    but sending a scam to your client or deleting their real mail will result in
    a $15 fine.'
