  m_text: 'Dear loyal Sangsong user,


    In need of a new phone? We have the perfect
    opportunity for you!


    We''re offering Sangsong users of over 10 years an
    opportunity for a free Sangsong Galactic S299 to celebrate our company''s 12th
    anniversery!


    The first 1,200 users to sign in via the link below and apply
    to recieve this gift will have it shipped to them within a week!


    Thank
    you,

    Sangsong'
