  m_text: "Review the list of common scam features which just appeared on the right
    side of your screen.         ---------------------------------------------------->\n\nCLICK
    on a feature to highlight it.\n\nAfterward, CLICK on a segment of the email on
    the left side of your screen to highlight it too. \n\nCLICK again to deselect.\n\n    
    - - - - - - - - - -     \n\nOnce you've highlighted both a feature and an email
    segment, your system will scan for whether the highlighted segment contains the
    given scam feature. \n\nUse this to help determine whether the email is a scam.
    \n\nYou'll recieve a $5 bonus for every feature discovered, but also a $1 fine
