  m_text: "You've finished your shift for the day. \nYou made $___.\n\nNow it's time
    to manage expenses. Use the money earned by your family to pay bills below. Click
    on...\n\nYour husband works in IT for a large corporation. \nHe earned $___ today.\n\nYour
